# Template macro for scintCube studies
/control/verbose 0
/run/verbose 0

##################### G4State_PreInit ###################

/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/addGeometryTo WaterBox 0
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/detectorID 0

# ================= ScintCube settings ===============

/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setSide **CubeSide** mm
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setMaterial **CubeMaterial**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setEnvelopeThickness 0.0 mm
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setEnvelopeMaterial G4_AIR
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setSplitAtInterface true
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setScintillationYield **ScintillationYield**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setBirksConstant **BirksConstant**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setLightCollectionEfficiency **LightCollectionEfficiency**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setDecayTime **DecayTime** ns
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setTransportDelay **TransportDelay** ns
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setTimeJitter **TimeJitter** ns
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setResolutionScale **ResolutionScale**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setPhotosensorType **PhotosensorType**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setDoseCalibrationFactor **DoseCalibrationFactor**
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/setDoseCalibrationFactorError **DoseCalibrationFactorError**

# ================= Phase Space settings ===============

/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/phsp/clearFiles
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/phsp/setPrefix **PhspPrefix**
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/setJaw1X **Jaw1X** cm
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/setJaw2X **Jaw2X** cm
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/setJaw1Y **Jaw1Y** cm
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/setJaw2Y **Jaw2Y** cm
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/rotateGantry **GantryAngle** deg
/MultiDetector1/beamline/clinac/rotateCollimator **CollimatorAngle** deg

##################### Initialization ###################

/run/initialize
/run/printProgress 10000

##################### G4State_Idle ###################

/MultiDetector1/run/SetMU **MU**
/MultiDetector1/phantoms/waterbox/phantomID 0
/MultiDetector1/phantoms/waterbox/translateTo 0 0 **WaterBoxZ** cm
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/detectorID 0
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/translateTo 0 0 **CubeZ** cm
/MultiDetector1/detectors/scintCube/rotateX **CubeAngle** deg

/control/execute mac/scorers1.mac
